    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting when you choose this tradition at 3rd level, you can use your ki to duplicate the effects of certain spells. As an action, you can spend 2 ki points to cast @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.S7VbUetIfVT7B6Eq]{Darkness}, @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.hJ6ZiA3fpoY8v9cp]{Darkvision}, @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.6UYMI5U6F1FHSGBH]{Pass Without Trace}, or @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.5VhqFROQYjr1P9lp]{Silence}, without providing material components. Additionally, you gain the @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.oIzA2MEHwxhtQneU]{Minor Illusion} cantrip if you don't already know it.</p>",
